Java

1. Spring cloud
	- Config server
		- supports feature flags
		- decouple release of software from launch/deployment of that software 
		- supports branch by abstraction and continues delivery pipelines
2. Eureka - Service Discovery
3. Zuul - micro proxy
4. Zipkin - Distributed tracing
5. Hystrix Circuit breaker - graceful degradation on reads
	- Monitor traffic with Hystrix dashboard
6. Spring cloud stream - graceful degradation on writes - gives eventual consistency
7. Netflix Simian Army
8. KS Kong - https://www.baeldung.com/kong
9. Spring notes
	- use constructor injection over member injection for unit test cases
	- Single constructor doesn't have to be annotated @Autowired
	- Configuration class can use @Autowired annotation